metadata.name: SUPER! | 2022 Twinny x Kiku's World by Sabet
metadata.description: As an open collaboration intended for the public, Sabet a talented visual artist, has welcomed artists from all backgrounds to incorporate, Kiku, a character created by Sabet himself, into their works. Twinny, a DJ/Producer, and visual artist gives his spin on Kiku through music and visual art. The song is produced, mix and mastered by Twinny Twin. The background illustration, and animation was done by Twinny Twin as well. Hereâ€™s SUPER!, an audio / visual NFT, from Twinny x Kiku's World by Sabet
